# 🎯 COMMAND: use
Description: Selects and loads a specific module or target into the active session by its search index.

Usage:
    use exploit <index> - Load an exploit module from your previous search results.
    use payload <index> - Load a payload module from your previous search results.
    use recon <index>   - Load a reconnaissance module from your previous search results.
    use target <index>  - Select a target from the saved targets list.

Note: Indices are dynamically generated. You must run the 'search' command first to obtain the correct index number before using this command.